code: import{GAME_CREATED,GAME_JOINED,GAME_PLAYED,GAME_REPLACED,GAME_REFRESHED,ROUND_ENDED}from"./types";export function gameCreated(gameName){return{type:GAME_CREATED,form:{gameName:gameName}};}export function gameJoined(gameName,creatorName){return{type:GAME_JOINED,form:{gameName:gameName,creatorName:creatorName}};}export function gamePlayed(gameName,creatorName){return{type:GAME_PLAYED,form:{gameName:gameName,creatorName:creatorName}};}export function gameReplaced(game){return{type:GAME_REPLACED,game:game};}export function gameRefreshed(){return{type:GAME_REFRESHED};}export function roundEnded(){return{type:ROUND_ENDED};}
